Package mstparser.io

Class Summary
CONLLReader A reader for files in CoNLL format.
CONLLWriter A writer to create files in CONLL format.
DependencyReader A class that defines common behavior and abstract methods for readers for different formats.
DependencyWriter A class that defines common behavior and abstract methods for writers for different formats.
MSTReader A reader for files in MST format.
MSTWriter A writer to create files in MST format.
